http://thepiratebay.org/torrent/5389144/The_Botanist_-_About_Ghosts_%282010%29

Worth buying imo, great artwork plus a DVD with 5.1 remix and documentary. But if you're expecting Death Metal, forget about it, this is called Heritage and is a sort of tribute to the 70's bands that have inspired Michael (Camel, Rainbow, Caravan). Plus, since Lindgren left the band it ain't the same. Still a perfect 10 as usual though ;D Thanx for sharing bro,
